{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't-- they didn't bother to come in and see what's what, because everybody was busy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as I remember, if there was anything-- I mean, if you cut-- if anything happened to you-- you cut your hand and you had to bleed and that was the hand you worked with-- maybe they allowed you to have to go and have a kind of a bandage with a little iodine.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because after all, you know, you couldn't go to work next day if you-- you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But basically, whoever was sick or in any way unfit for heavy labor just was-- was totally dismissed as a human being, as a person, as anything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't count anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one way or another, he was gotten rid of, whether by shooting by the Ukrainian, or by shooting by the Gestapo, or by-- by-- by being taken out with 20 other men into the woods and being shot there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- as a matter of fact, there were a number of very small children smuggled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a young kid, but there were younger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were kids five, six years--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by then I was about 13.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were five and six-year-old kids that they even survived Auschwitz, believe it or not, the kids from my home town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't survive later, past that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Past the liberation, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they did survive that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said, the-- the evacuation of-- of-- the liquidation of the town was in October, 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the camp lasted until the end of June, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you see, what happened is that there was a kind of a rebellion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't really a rebellion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you know, our-- the camp was surrounded with guards and-- in the towers, on the towers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And very soon-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, could that-- could have been about July.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Could have been July.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The camp at Majowka was totally evacuated to another camp which was nearer to the-- to the-- nearer to the factory and near a siding, near a railroad siding.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was after.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, first was Strzelnica, then was Majowka, then was just Majowka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, in 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the one camp that was still in existence, about May, let's say, was Majowka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now they liquidated Majowka, and they took us to an adjacent-- to a camp that was neither Strzelnica nor Majowka, but another camp that was very near the railroad siding.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, of course, they again-- they had the guards and the towers and the dogs and all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And talk was, nobody went to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And talk was that there's going to be-- and I think prob-- we stayed there, probably, only a few days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the talk was that we were going to be shipped somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the night before-- we didn't know that the next day, whatever that next day was to be-- but on a particular night, what happened to be the night before we were sent out of that last camp, a lot of the young fellows in-- in the-- young fellows and strong women, too, within the camp decided, no more.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, the Germans started shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were heaps of people because there were maybe only two openings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Heaps of people piled up next to the opening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That night, of course, I-- I-- we didn't escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
